This page demonstrates another embedded Python code cell that computes a quick summary.


import pandas as pd
sales = pd.Series([12.5, 15.2, 14.0, 18.3, 19.1, 21.4, 17.8]) summary = { “count”: sales.count(), “mean”: round(sales.mean(), 2), “std”: round(sales.std(), 2), “min”: float(sales.min()), “max”: float(sales.max()) } summary
